## 8. Lipinski Ro5 + Veber drug-likeness audit (v6 land 2026-05-10)

방법: hand-heuristic (rdkit 미설치 — local Mac). MW/logP/HBD/HBA 추정 — Phase β 에 정밀 audit (rdkit + TPSA + RotB + formal charge + Lipinski violations) 권장. Veber: TPSA<140 + RotB<10 (본 audit 미포함, 후속 ramp).

| ID                  | SMILES (heavy)                                                       | est. MW | est. logP | HBD | HBA | Ro5 verdict |
|---------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------|---------|-----------|-----|-----|-------------|
| `hxq-cmt-hd6-001`   | `OC(=O)c1ccc(NC(=O)CN2C(=S)NN=C2c2ccccc2)cc1` (22)                  | ~289    | ~1.5      | 2   | 7   | ✅ PASS     |
| `hxq-cmt-clc1-001`  | `OC(=O)c1ccccc1Nc1ccc(C(F)(F)F)nc1F` (17)                            | ~300    | ~2.5      | 2   | 6   | ✅ PASS     |
| `hxq-cmt-sar1-001`  | `Nc1nc2cc(F)c(F)cc2c(=O)n1Cc1ccncc1` (17)                            | ~289    | ~1.5      | 1   | 5   | ✅ PASS     |
| `hxq-cmt-mfn2-001`  | `O=C(NC1CCCCC1NC(=O)c1cccnc1)c1cccnc1` (19)                          | ~324    | ~1.8      | 2   | 6   | ✅ PASS     |
| `hxq-als-hd6-001`   | `Cc1ccc(NC(=O)CN2C(=S)NN=C2c2ccccc2)cc1` (20)                        | ~323    | ~3.0      | 1   | 4   | ✅ PASS (BBB 적합) |

핵심: CMT hd6-001 (말초 한정, logP ~1.5) ↔ ALS hd6-001 (CNS-penetrant, logP ~3.0) — 의도된 BBB design 차이가 Ro5 audit 에서도 정합. 5/5 PASS. ALS sar1-001 = CMT sar1-001 SMILES 동일 (BBB audit 별도 ID).

ASO/AAV/Fc-fusion/PLGA-nanocarrier (5종) 은 small-molecule Ro5 적용 NA — biologic/oligo guideline 별도 (예: GalNAc-siRNA 의 dosing PK / AAV titer + 면역원성 / Fc-fusion 의 반감기) 가 후속 ramp.

