## 9. Biologic / oligo / AAV / Fc-fusion / nano modality guideline audit (v7 land 2026-05-11)

방법: 공개 가이드라인 (FDA cell/gene therapy 2024, ICH Q6B, USP <1059>, oligonucleotide therapeutics FDA draft 2024) 기반 modality-별 정성 audit. small-mol Ro5 적용 NA 후보 8 entry. 정량 PK simulation / cGMP 적합성 audit 은 wet-lab + 외부 도구 필요 (별도 ramp).

### 9.1. ASO / siRNA cohort (4 entry)

| ID                   | modality                   | delivery     | typical dose          | t½ (tissue)     | dosing freq    | key PK liability                              | manufacturability | audit |
|----------------------|----------------------------|--------------|-----------------------|------------------|----------------|------------------------------------------------|-------------------|-------|
| `hxq-cmt-pmp22-001`  | siRNA 21-nt + SQ/지방산 conj | SC          | 5-15 mg/kg q4w (예상) | ~2-4w (말초신경) | 월 1회 SC      | Schwann uptake = novel (GalNAc 등가물 없음)  | mid (lipid conj 표준화 필요) | NEEDS-WORK |
| `hxq-cmt-pmp22-002`  | gapmer ASO 18-mer (PS+MOE) | SC or IT     | 12-25 mg IT q3m       | ~1-2m (말초신경) | 분기 1회 IT    | splice-modulating selectivity, HNPP overshoot | high (Sarepta/Ionis paradigm) | PASS-conditional |
| `hxq-als-stmn2-001`  | gapmer ASO 18-mer (PS+MOE) | IT           | 25-100 mg IT q3-4m    | ~2-3m (CSF/CNS)  | 분기 1회 IT    | cryptic exon 5'ss block, canonical exon spare | high (QurAlis QRL-101 paradigm) | PASS-conditional |
| `hxq-als-atxn2-001`  | gapmer ASO 18-mer (PS+MOE) | IT           | 25-100 mg IT q3-4m    | ~2-3m (CSF/CNS)  | 분기 1회 IT    | ATXN1/ATXN3 paralog avoid (≥500x)             | high (Stanford-Lilly paradigm) | PASS-conditional |

핵심 audit (4 entry):
- PS+MOE backbone (Phosphorothioate + 2'-MOE wing) = 표준 gapmer 5-10-5 paradigm. 합성/CMC 표준화됨 → manufacturability HIGH.
- pmp22-001 siRNA + Schwann uptake = open question — GalNAc-asialoglycoprotein 받침이 hepatic limited, Schwann 신경전달엔 적용 안됨. 대안: 지방산 (예: C18-palmitate) conjugate / squalene (SQ) ‒ ALN-RSV-class 검증된 SC 흡수. 그러나 Schwann selectivity 는 별도 평가 (perineurium barrier 우회 검증 필요).
- pmp22-002 ASO splice modulation: HNPP overshoot 회피 = 50-60% knockdown ceiling 필수. Falsifier F-novel-cmt-schematic-X 의 일부.
- stmn2-001 / atxn2-001 IT gapmer: ALS CSF-CNS 침투 표준 paradigm (Tofersen / QRL-101 검증). F-novel-als-vqe-6/7 와 cross-link.

### 9.2. Fc-fusion + AAV + nano cohort (4 entry)

| ID                   | modality                                | delivery | typical dose         | t½              | dosing freq     | key liability                                       | manufacturability | audit |
|----------------------|-----------------------------------------|----------|-----------------------|------------------|------------------|------------------------------------------------------|-------------------|-------|
| `hxq-cmt-nrg1-001`   | NRG1-III EGF + Fc + Schwann-target pep  | IV/SC    | 0.5-3 mg/kg q2w       | ~10-21d (Fc·FcRn) | 2주 1회         | full agonist toxicity (Schwann remyelin 과흥분)     | mid (Fc-fusion 표준 + peptide conj 추가) | NEEDS-WORK |
| `hxq-cmt-fig4-001`   | AAV9-CAG-FIG4-WPRE + 4×miR-122 BS       | IT       | 1E13-3E14 vg/kg 1회   | 영구 (gene)      | 1회 (재투여 불가) | pre-existing AAV9 면역원성 (~30-40% 인구), liver detarget | high (AAV9 GMP capacity 충분) | PASS-conditional |
| `hxq-cmt-nano-001`   | PLGA-PEG 50-80nm + Schwann ligand + pH-shed | SC/IV    | 1-5 mg/kg q1-2w        | ~3-14d (PLGA 분해) | 주 1회-격주     | Schwann ligand selectivity (perineurium 우회 검증)  | mid (cGMP nano 표준화 진행 중)              | NEEDS-WORK |
| `hxq-als-nano-001`   | PLGA-PEG + ChAT/SMI-32 ligand + IT + pH-shed | IT       | 5-20 mg IT q1m         | ~7-21d (PLGA 분해) | 월 1회 IT       | motor neuron selectivity (oligo/astro detarget), retrograde 흐름 | mid (cGMP) | NEEDS-WORK |

핵심 audit (4 entry):
- nrg1-001 Fc-fusion: FcRn 의존 ~3주 t½, full agonist 회피 → partial agonist clip (EGF domain mutation) 필수. F-novel-cmt-schematic-X.
- fig4-001 AAV9 + miR-122 BS: liver detarget 표준 paradigm (Spark, Voyager 검증), pre-existing immunity 30-40% (population coverage 한계). 1회 투여 → 평생 효과.
- nano-001 (CMT/ALS): cGMP PLGA-PEG 표준화 진행 중 (NCI Nanotechnology Characterization Lab). Schwann/motor-neuron ligand selectivity = 별도 wet-lab 평가 필요.

### 9.3. Schematic-only DESIGN small-mol (4 entry — SMILES 대기)

다음 후보는 small-mol 이지만 SMILES placeholder 미land (scaffold class TBD), Phase β SMILES commit 후 §8 Ro5 audit 합류 예정:

- `hxq-cmt-gjb1-001` — Cx32 mutant-selective fold-rescue (scaffold class TBD)
