## 12. F-Q-6-B/C 양자 Hamiltonian build + VQE (v7 land 2026-05-11)

방법: `_qiskit_bridge/module/pocket_active_space.py` + `tests/quantum_{h2o,drug}_vqe_v7.py`. qiskit 2.4.1 + qiskit-nature 0.7.2 + qiskit-algorithms 0.4.0 + pyscf 2.13.0 + rdkit 2026.3.1. Active space = 2e/2o 또는 4e/4o (HOMO/LUMO frontier, NOT pocket-restricted). VQE = EfficientSU2 depth=1 + COBYLA 400 iters + COBYLA tol 1e-8 + seed 7 random initial point + StatevectorEstimator V2.

honest scope: 본 §12 = **build pipeline validation + frontier-orbital VQE** 까지. 실제 drug-target binding 평가는 pocket-restricted active space (F-Q-6-D ramp, catalytic residue orbital indices 명시) 필수 — 본 §12 산출 energy 는 frontier 2e/2o 의 isolated 분자 ground state delta, **binding 와 무관**.

