#### 12.1.b. UCCSD reps=1 (F-Q-6-B2 closure ramp — v7 Phase β)

EfficientSU2 depth=1 의 B2 8.36 mHa fail → qiskit-nature UCCSD ansatz (HF initial state + reps=1, 26-param 6-qubit) + ParityMapper 동일 active space 재시도. 3 optimizer 비교:

