| `sar1-002-B`                    | alt-B + 6-Cl                                  | 1.61 | 86.69  | ❌  | 3.39               | logP 미달                               |
| `sar1-002-C`                    | alt-B + 6-Me                                  | 1.26 | 86.69  | ❌  | 23.6               | logP 미달                               |
| `sar1-002-D`                    | alt-B + 7-cyclopropyl                         | 1.83 | 86.69  | ❌  | 2.27               | logP 미달                               |
| `sar1-002-E`                    | alt-B + 6-CF3 + p-CF3-benzyl (pyridyl→aryl)   | 3.60 | 73.80  | ❌  | 91.8               | logP 초과 (>3.5)                        |
| `sar1-002-F`                    | alt-B + 6-CF3 + naphthyl-1-methyl             | 3.73 | 73.80  | ❌  | 3.68               | logP 초과                               |
| ⭐ `hxq-als-sar1-002-G`         | **alt-B + 6-CF3 + benzyl (pyridyl→aryl)**     | **2.58** | **73.80** | **✅** | **14.7**       | **BBB PASS + IP novel ⭐ ALS 권장**     |
| `sar1-002-H`                    | alt-B + 3,5-bis-CF3-benzyl                    | 3.60 | 73.80  | ❌  | **0.45** ⭐        | sub-µHa frontier, but logP 초과         |

⭐ **결론**: `hxq-als-sar1-002-G` = alt-B core 위 `6-CF3` + `N-benzyl` (pyridyl→phenyl 변환 + 1개 lipophilic 치환) → ALS BBB target (logP 2.58, TPSA 73.8, HBD 1, MW 338.08) 정합 + IP-novel (Disarm/Lilly 회피) + chem-acc PASS. **v5 의 "ALS sar1 = CMT sar1 동일" 가정 무효화 → `hxq-als-sar1-002-G` 별도 land**.

#### 12.2.f.ii. hxq-als-c9orf72-001 scaffold class 해소 (G4C2 RNA secondary structure binder)

5 schematic-only 후보 중 첫 번째 scaffold land — G4-quadruplex / hairpin binder paradigm:

| ID                              | scaffold class                                          | logP | TPSA   | BBB | 2e/2o delta (µHa) | comment                                |
|---------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|------|--------|-----|--------------------|-----------------------------------------|
| ⭐ `hxq-als-c9orf72-001-A`     | 9-amino-N-(dimethylamino-ethyl)acridine (BRACO-19 시뮬)  | 3.36 | 28.16  | ✅  | 14.9               | logP 3.36 + TPSA 28 (BBB 강함)         |
| `hxq-als-c9orf72-001-B`        | 3-amino-9-(piperidinyl-ethyl-amino)acridine             | 3.87 | 54.18  | ❌  | 28.3               | logP 초과                               |
| ⭐ `hxq-als-c9orf72-001-C`     | **indole-2-carboxamide + piperidine-propyl (DC-34 시뮬)** | **2.77** | **48.13** | **✅** | **21.9**     | **BBB PASS + 가장 잘 알려진 G4 RNA scaffold ⭐** |

⭐ **결론**: 두 후보 모두 BBB PASS — `c9orf72-001-C` (DC-34 paradigm, indole-piperidine carboxamide) 가 G4 RNA 특이성 lit precedent (Su et al. Nature 2014) 가장 강함. `c9orf72-001-A` (acridine class) 는 보조 alternative. **`hxq-als-c9orf72-001` 최종 SMILES = variant C** 권장.

honest scope: c9orf72-001-C 의 G4C2 RNA selectivity 는 wet-lab 검증 필수 (RNA secondary structure 결합 affinity, off-target G4 회피, BIIB078 ASO fail 회피 small-mol paradigm 입증). 본 land = scaffold class 가 land 된 첫 번째 small-mol c9orf72 candidate — Phase β 의 4e/4o UCCSD + pocket VQE ramp 자격 확보.

