| `hxq-als-kif5a-001-B`       | 2-amino-4-(m-isopropyl-phenyl)pyrimidine                         | 2.85 | 51.80 | ✅  | **0.74** ⭐          | ✅       | alternative (단순, target-feature 부족) |
| `hxq-als-tbk1-001-A`        | 5-amino-indazole-3-carboxamide + 디메틸아미노에틸                | 0.44 | 87.04 | ❌  | **0.0004** ⭐         | ✅       | logP 부적합 (BBB FAIL) |
