## 13. Biologic cohort 정밀화 — ASO seed + AAV capsid + Fc-fusion + nano cargo (v7 closure)

§9 modality guideline 의 정성 audit 위에 구체 sequence / composition heuristic 추가. ASO seed sequence + AAV9 de-imm variant + Fc-fusion peptide tag + PLGA nano cargo specs 모두 **공개 chemoinformatics / lit precedent** 기반 — wet-lab 검증 0건, 임상 0건 disclaimer 유지.

### 13.1. ASO/siRNA cohort — seed sequence heuristic (4 entry)

ASO/siRNA seed design 의 정합성은 (1) target mRNA secondary structure 위 accessible site, (2) paralog cross-reactivity 회피, (3) PS+MOE backbone 의 안정성 + immune escape, (4) IT delivery PK 의존. 본 §13.1 = sequence design heuristic (precise BLAST + UNAFold/RNAhybrid 는 wet-lab side).

| ID                    | target mRNA region          | seed 길이 | backbone        | paradigm 참조                 | 핵심 design 고려                                                |
|-----------------------|------------------------------|------------|------------------|--------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------|
| `hxq-cmt-pmp22-001`   | PMP22 mRNA 3'UTR allele-selective region (R98 분기, NM_000304) | 21 nt siRNA seed (passenger 19 nt + 2 nt overhang) | OMe + SQ 지방산 conjugate (Schwann uptake) | DTx-1252 (DTx Pharma/Novartis FALCON), Sarepta CMT1A AAV NT-3 paradigm | (a) PMP22 mut allele 만 cleavage — WT PMP22 보존 (HNPP overshoot 회피) (b) seed region GC 40-60% (c) RISC loading bias (5' U 또는 A) |
| `hxq-cmt-pmp22-002`   | PMP22 pre-mRNA exon 3 / intron 2-3 splice junction               | gapmer 18-mer 5-10-5 (PS+MOE wing + DNA gap) | PS backbone (RNase H 활성) + 2'-MOE wing (off-target 회피) | Tofersen (SOD1 ASO) FDA 2023 paradigm | (a) splice modulation — intron 2-3 splice site 강화 (b) gapmer DNA gap 으로 RNase H cleavage, MOE wing 으로 selectivity (c) HNPP overshoot 50-60% KD ceiling |
| `hxq-als-stmn2-001`   | STMN2 pre-mRNA cryptic exon (TDP-43 LoF inclusion 차단) | gapmer 18-mer 5-10-5 (PS+MOE) | PS+MOE 표준 | QurAlis QRL-101 ALS Phase 1 | (a) cryptic exon 5'ss block (TDP-43 LoF condition) (b) canonical exon 절약 (c) STMN1/STMN3 paralog 회피 |
| `hxq-als-atxn2-001`   | ATXN2 mRNA 5'UTR / CDS                              | gapmer 18-mer 5-10-5 (PS+MOE) | PS+MOE 표준 | Stanford-Lilly ATXN2 ASO Phase 1 (NCT04494256) | (a) polyQ ATXN2 mRNA 50% KD → TDP-43 항상성 회복 (b) ATXN1 / ATXN3 paralog ≥500x 선택성 (c) IT delivery, IT 3-4 month dosing |

honest scope: 본 §13.1 의 4 entry = sequence design **고려사항** 만 (구체 nt sequence 아님). 실제 seed = (1) target mRNA full sequence + UNAFold secondary structure + (2) BLAST/RNAhybrid paralog audit + (3) RISC loading 시뮬레이션 + (4) 합성/HPLC purification + (5) wet-lab GAP-NMS / iPSC-motor neuron / Schwann 세포 KD efficacy + paralog cross-rxn. 본 audit = paradigm comparator + modality 정합 까지.

### 13.2. AAV9 capsid de-immunization variant (fig4-001)

`hxq-cmt-fig4-001` (AAV9-CAG-FIG4-WPRE + 4×miR-122 BS) 의 capsid de-immunization heuristic:

| variant                       | parent                       | de-imm 핵심 mutation                | population coverage 예상          | tropism                                  |
|-------------------------------|------------------------------|--------------------------------------|------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| AAV9 wild-type                | natural                      | (none)                               | seropositive ~30-40% → 우회 불가  | broad CNS + 척수 + 근육 + 간 (off-target) |
| AAV-PHP.eB                    | AAV9-Y733F                   | VP3 surface loop AA587-590 변형      | seropositive 비율 약간 감소        | mouse CNS-enhanced (인간 NA)              |
| AAVrh.10                      | rhesus AAV10                 | natural rhesus-derived               | seropositive ~10% (인간 cross-rxn) | CNS strong + motor neuron retrograde      |
| **AAV9.HSC-NL10** (heuristic) | AAV9 capsid VR-IV substitution | VP3 외부 loop 3 잔기 변형 (lit-class 5×) | seropositive 인구 ~70% → ~30% 회복 | AAV9 tropism 유사 + de-imm                |
| **AAV-PHP.B.K** (heuristic)   | AAV-PHP.B + K humanization   | VP3 R346K / N395K humanization      | human BBB 침투 평가 (mouse hot)    | CNS + motor neuron (humanized)            |

honest scope: variant selection = lit precedent + computational structure 기반 heuristic. 실제 de-imm validation = (1) human serum cross-rxn assay (50 patient cohort), (2) capsid AlphaFold + bioinformatics neutralizing epitope mapping, (3) NHP IT delivery + 18 month durability, (4) DSMC + IND-ready 안전성. 본 audit = paradigm comparator 까지.

### 13.3. Fc-fusion peptide tag heuristic (nrg1-001)

`hxq-cmt-nrg1-001` (NRG1-III EGF + Fc + Schwann-target peptide) 의 Schwann-target peptide heuristic:

| Schwann surface marker          | peptide tag heuristic                                  | binding mode                | half-life impact          |
|----------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------|----------------------------|
| ErbB2-3 (NRG1 native receptor)   | NRG1-III EGF domain (~60 aa) — full agonist 위험       | direct ligand                | Fc-FcRn ~3 weeks            |
| Cx32 (gap junction, CMT1X 양립) | Connexin-binding peptide (P2X4-class, ~20 aa)         | surface anchor               | minimal Fc 영향             |
| **P0 (MPZ)** Schwann marker     | **MPZ extracellular domain mimic (8-15 aa)** ⭐         | Schwann-specific             | Fc-FcRn ~3 weeks            |
| **MBP/PMP22 surface region**    | MBP cytoplasmic loop mimic (NA — surface 노출 없음)   | NA                           | NA                          |
| LGR4/5 (Schwann progenitor)     | LGR4 ligand R-spondin tag (~30 aa)                    | surface anchor               | Fc-FcRn ~3 weeks            |

⭐ **P0 (MPZ) Schwann-target tag 권장** — Schwann 세포 가장 특이적 surface marker, 8-15 aa extracellular peptide 추가만으로 Schwann selectivity 확보. 심근/유방 ErbB2 회피 (트라스투주맙 cardiotoxicity 교훈).

honest scope: peptide tag sequence 정밀화 = (1) P0 extracellular domain crystal structure (PDB 1NEU) + binding loop 식별, (2) AlphaFold 로 Fc-peptide-target 3-way 안정성 simulation, (3) in vitro Schwann 세포 binding ELISA, (4) NRG1-III partial agonist 강도 (Schwann 과증식 = schwannoma 위험 회피). 본 audit = 5 candidate paradigm까지.

### 13.4. PLGA-PEG nano cargo + ligand specs (nano-001 CMT + ALS)

`hxq-cmt-nano-001` (Schwann perineurium) + `hxq-als-nano-001` (motor neuron IT) PLGA-PEG specs:

| spec axis                      | cmt-nano-001 (SC)                                     | als-nano-001 (IT)                                  |
|---------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------|
| size                            | 50-80 nm (perineurium TJ 침투, RES 회피 >200nm)        | 50-100 nm (IT CSF 안정 + motor neuron retrograde)  |
| PLGA lactide/glycolide ratio    | 50:50 (3-7일 분해, Schwann uptake 기간)                | 50:50 또는 65:35 (14-21일 분해, IT 장기 stable)    |
| PEG MW + density                | 5 kDa + brush regime (RES 회피 + Schwann 침투 균형)   | 2 kDa + low density (IT injection 후 cell uptake)  |
| pH-responsive 분해               | extracellular pH 7.4 stable, lysosomal pH 5 분해 (Schwann uptake 후 cargo release) | extracellular CSF pH 7.4 stable, motor neuron axoplasm pH 7 stable, lysosomal pH 5 분해 |
| **Schwann/motor neuron ligand** ⭐ | **P0/MPZ-binding peptide** (Schwann 특이) | **ChAT/SMI-32 motor neuron 마커 peptide** + **kinesin-1 binding** (axonal retrograde) |
| cargo modular options           | pmp22 siRNA (4-5 mg/mL) / hd6 small mol / NT-3 peptide | SOD1 ASO / hxq-als-{hd6,sar1,c9orf72}-001 / SMN2 splice mod |
| dosing 경로                    | SC q1-2w (1-5 mg/kg)                                   | IT q1m (5-20 mg)                                    |

honest scope: nano spec 정밀화 = (1) NCI Nanotechnology Characterization Lab (NCL) cGMP audit, (2) cryo-EM + DLS 정량 size + surface coverage, (3) Schwann 세포 in vitro uptake + perineurium TJ ex vivo perfusion, (4) NHP IT injection + 18 month motor neuron retention. 본 audit = paradigm 정의 까지.

### 13.5. F-novel falsifier closure (§13 cumulative)

- F-novel-cmt-schematic-X (pmp22-001/002, gjb1-001, nrg1-001, fig4-001, nano-001) — §13.1-4 paradigm 정밀화 + §12.2.g gjb1 small-mol scaffold 해소
- F-novel-als-build-{6,7} (stmn2-001 + atxn2-001) — §13.1 paradigm 정밀화
- F-novel-als-nano + cross — §13.4 spec axis 정합 + cargo modular 정의

이상 ASO seed + AAV capsid + Fc-tag + nano cargo = **5 biologic candidate (pmp22-001/002, nrg1-001, fig4-001, cmt-nano-001, als-nano-001) + 2 ALS ASO (stmn2-001, atxn2-001)** paradigm 정밀화 완료. wet-lab 검증 + 임상 0건 disclaimer 유지.

