⚠️ **ADMET 진짜 측정 (PAMPA-BBB / P-gp efflux / CYP1A2/2D6/3A4 inhibition)** = wet-lab 측정 필수, rdkit-only 으로 closure 불가. SwissADME web 도구 가 일부 보조 가능 (browser-based).

### 15.2. Pocket VQE (item 1 PARTIAL) — HDAC6 cluster QM 첫 attempt

⭐ **F-Q-6-D 첫 진입 입증** — `tests/hdac6_pocket_vqe_v7.py` (cluster QM mini model):

cluster: `[Zn(II) + imidazole + acetate + hydroxamate]` (HDAC6 active site mimic)
- net charge -1, spin 0, 27 atoms (138 electrons)
- imidazole = His mimic (Zn-binding)
- acetate = Asp mimic
- hydroxamate = Tubastatin-class ZBG mimic

결과:
- n_qubits=6, n_pauli=325, basis=sto-3g, active space 4e/4o frontier
- CASCI = -2481.685 Ha (full active-space reference)
- VQE UCCSD reps=1 SLSQP = -2481.685 Ha
- delta = **15.0 µHa** ✅ **chem-acc PASS** (sub-µHa FAIL)
- build wall 19s + VQE wall 76s

honest 함의:
- ✅ **pocket-restricted active space pipeline 작동 입증** — Zn(II) coordination 환경에서도 chem-acc 도달.
- ⚠️ sto-3g basis 는 transition metal Zn 의 d-orbital 표현 한계 — def2-svp 또는 lanl2dz ECP 필요 (compute cost ↑).
- ⚠️ active space 4e/4o = full cluster frontier — Zn d-orbital + ligand orbital 명시적 선정 (active_orbital_indices) 미적용.
- ⚠️ cluster QM ≠ 실 HDAC6 — 단백질 잔기 전체 + co-crystal binding mode 는 QM/MM 또는 explicit truncation 필요.
- ✅ pipeline 자체 (qiskit-nature ActiveSpaceTransformer + ParityMapper + UCCSD + SLSQP) 가 metal-ligand cluster 에 generalize 됨.

next ramp (외부 도구 + 실 target 의존):
- PDB 5W5K (HDAC6) 또는 5G0F (HDAC6+TSA) 다운로드 + biopython 잔기 parse
- truncated active site 4-5 Å + capping residue + hydrogen 추가
- def2-svp 또는 6-31G basis 로 build (compute ~10-100x)
- explicit active_orbital_indices (Zn 3d + ligand HOMO/LUMO)
- F-Q-6-D sub-falsifier set 신설

