### 15.3. IP clearance heuristic (item 2 PARTIAL) — 공개 chemoinformatics 검색 query map

실제 freedom-to-operate (FTO) 평가 = 5소 cross-check + 변리사 의견 필수. 본 §15.3 = **공개 chemoinformatics 검색 query 정의** (heuristic, paradigm-only).

검색 query map (5 small-mol + 4 alt scaffold class):

| scaffold class                        | SureChEMBL query (EMBL-EBI free)                  | Espacenet query (EPO free)           | Google Patents query (free)             |
|----------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------|------------------------------------------|
| 1,3,4-thiadiazol-2(3H)-thione HDAC ZBG | `"thiadiazol thione" HDAC6 OR HDAC inhibitor`     | `ti=thiadiazolone AND cl=A61K`        | `thiadiazolone HDAC6 inhibitor`         |
| 1,3,4-oxadiazol-2(3H)-one HDAC ZBG    | `"oxadiazolone" HDAC OR histone deacetylase`      | `ti=oxadiazolone AND cl=A61P`          | `oxadiazolone HDAC inhibitor`           |
| 2-anilinobenzoic acid ClC-1            | `"anilinobenzoic" chloride channel`               | `ti=anilinobenzoate AND cl=A61K31`     | `anilinobenzoate chloride channel`      |
| 2-aminonicotinic acid                 | `"aminonicotinic" channel OR kidney`               | `ti=aminonicotinic AND cl=A61K`         | `aminonicotinic acid channel modulator` |
| 2-amino-quinazolin-4-one SARM1 TIR    | `quinazolinone SARM1 OR TIR domain NAD+`           | `ti=quinazolinone AND ic=C07D`         | `quinazolinone SARM1 inhibitor`          |
| pyrido[2,3-d]pyrimidin-4-one          | `pyrido pyrimidinone SARM1 OR Wallerian`          | `ti=pyridopyrimidinone AND cl=A61P25`  | `pyridopyrimidinone neuroprotection`    |
| diamine + bis-nicotinamide MFN2       | `mitofusin OR MFN2 small molecule`                 | `ti=mitofusin AND cl=A61K`              | `mitofusin agonist small molecule`      |
| pyrrolidin + pyrazinecarboxamide      | `pyrrolidinyl pyrazinamide GTPase`                | `ti=pyrrolidinyl AND ic=A61K31`         | `pyrrolidinyl pyrazinecarboxamide`      |
| 4-CF3-aryl piperidinyl-carboxamide chaperone | `connexin Cx32 chaperone OR fold-rescue`     | `ti=connexin AND cl=A61K`               | `Cx32 chaperone CMT1X`                  |

honest:
- ✅ query map = pubic database 의 search entry point — 5소 cross-check 의 첫 단계
- ❌ 실제 FTO verdict (cleared / not cleared) = variant claim language 분석 + 변리사 의견 (수일~수주 + 비용 ~$5K-$50K)
- ❌ 보호되지 않은 (out of patent) chemotype 인지 검증 = lit precedent + 출원/등록일 cross-check

next ramp:
- SureChEMBL bulk download → BLAST chemotype search 자동화
- Google Patents API (~$0.10/query) 또는 free Espacenet OPS API (5000/min)
- 변리사 retainer (CMT 5 chemotype × 5 territory cross-check ~$25K-50K)

### 15.4. Selectivity reference (item 3) — wet-lab paradigm 만, 실측 0건

CMT 5 small-mol target 의 paralog selectivity 표준 + reference compound (wet-lab 실측 0건, 본 audit = paradigm 만):

| target            | paralog selectivity 목표 | reference 화합물 (실측 data lit 참조)           | 측정 protocol (wet-lab)                             |
|-------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|
| HDAC6 (hd6)       | HDAC1/2/3 ≥1000x          | ACY-1215 (Citarinostat, ~500x); Tubastatin A (~1000x); SR-3677 | 11 HDAC isoform enzyme assay (BPS Bioscience / Reaction Biology Corp panel) |
| ClC-1 (clc1)      | ClC-2/ClC-K ≥500x         | 9-AC (anthracene-9-carboxylic acid); NMD670 (NMD Pharma) | patch-clamp electrophysiology, HEK293-CFTR/ClC family transfection |
| SARM1 TIR (sar1)  | non-TIR NAD-utilizing enzymes (CD38, NADase) ≥500x | DSRM-3716 (Disarm/Lilly); 7-CSeR; nicotinamide variants | NAD+ hydrolysis kinetics + selectivity panel       |
| MFN2 (mfn2)       | MFN1/Drp1 (wild-type MFN2) ≥500x; R94Q allele bias | MASM7 (mitofusin agonist peptide); no small-mol disclosed | mito fusion assay (PEG-mediated mito coalescence + MFN2 R94Q rescue) |
| Cx32 (gjb1)       | Cx26/Cx43 wild-type fold ≥1000x; Cx32 mutant 만 rescue | Ataluren (readthrough, different mechanism); VX-770 paradigm (CFTR corrector) | dye transfer assay (Lucifer yellow) in Cx32-iPSC Schwann |

honest:
- ✅ reference 화합물 + protocol = paradigm comparator 표준
- ❌ 본 9 후보 (5 orig + 4 alt) 의 selectivity = **wet-lab 실측 0건** — 본 audit 닫힘 의미 아님
- ❌ wet-lab cost (CMT 9 후보 × 5 target × selectivity panel ~30-100 화합물 cross-test) = ~$50K-200K + 3-6 month

### 15.5. BBB / Schwann perineurium / IT 침투 (item 4) — heuristic + paradigm 만

heuristic prediction (rdkit-based):

| ID                        | logP (rdkit) | TPSA  | HBD | rule-of-thumb BBB         | rule-of-thumb P-gp           |
|---------------------------|---------------|-------|-----|----------------------------|--------------------------------|
| `hxq-cmt-hd6-001-orig`    | 2.94          | 100   | 3   | ⚠️ TPSA 100 ↑ → 침투 어려움 (말초 한정 intent 정합) | 가능성 ↑ (말초 한정 적합)     |
| `hxq-cmt-clc1-001-orig`   | 3.68          | 62    | 2   | ⚠️ logP 3.68 ↑ → CNS leak 가능 | P-gp 보강 필요                |
| `hxq-cmt-sar1-001-orig`   | 1.70          | 74    | 1   | ⚠️ logP 1.7 낮음 → CNS 안전 (CMT 적합) | P-gp 무관                  |
| `hxq-cmt-mfn2-001-orig`   | 1.95          | 84    | 2   | ⚠️ TPSA 84 + logP 1.95 → CNS 적합 (intent 정합) | P-gp 무관                |
| `hxq-cmt-gjb1-001-A`      | 3.31          | 32    | 1   | ✅ logP 3.31 + TPSA 32 → BBB 적합 (BBB 무관 IT 이지만) | P-gp 무관 |

honest:
- ✅ rdkit logP + TPSA + HBD = rule-of-thumb screen (Lipinski-Veber 외 BBB-focused heuristic)
- ❌ PAMPA-BBB Pe (×10⁻⁶ cm/s) 실측 = MultiScreen Permeability Filter Plate 시스템 (~$5K + 1주)
- ❌ P-gp efflux ratio (MDCK-MDR1 transwell) = wet-lab 실측 ~$3K/화합물 + 2주
- ❌ Schwann perineurium ex vivo perfusion = nerve explant 모델, 전문 lab (~$10K + 4-6 week)
- ❌ IT delivery PK (CSF concentration vs time) = NHP IT injection cohort ~$200K + 18 month

### 15.6. IND-ready CMC + 임상 1-3상 (item 5) — paradigm doc 만, 닫힘 불가

CMT 신약의 임상 진입 pathway (FDA / EMA / 식약처 기준):

| 단계              | timeline | cost (소분자 추정)    | endpoint + sample size                                    | 본 후보 적용 가능성       |
|-------------------|----------|------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|----------------------------|
| **IND-enabling**  | 1-2 년   | $5-15M                 | CMC + GLP toxicology (rat + dog 28d, GLP rep) + DMPK + 안정성 + IND filing | ❌ 본 9 후보 모두 wet-lab 검증 0건 — 진입 전 |
| **Phase 1**       | 1-1.5 년 | $5-10M                 | 안전성 + PK (healthy volunteer 20-100, single + multi-ascending dose) | ❌ |
| **Phase 2a/b**    | 2-3 년   | $20-50M                | CMT1A/2 환자 50-200 cohort, CMTNS / ONLS / NCV biomarker (12-24 month follow-up) | ❌ |
| **Phase 3**       | 3-5 년   | $50-200M               | CMT global 300-1000 환자 multi-center RCT, primary endpoint MFN-Pro+ CMTNS 변화 | ❌ |
| **NDA / MAA / 식약처** | 1-2 년 | $5-20M                 | 자료 제출 + 심사 + 출시                                    | ❌ |
| **post-market**   | 영구     | $5-20M/year            | Phase 4 safety, CMT registry, real-world evidence         | ❌ |

총 timeline: **~7-12 년**, **~$100-300M** per candidate, 임상 1상 → NDA 성공률 **~9%** (rare disease).

honest:
- ❌ 본 v7 = 임상 진입 **약 7-12 년 전** 단계 (DESIGN/build 단계)
- ❌ IND filing 자체가 paradigm 의미 없는 외부 task (FDA submission system + 변호사 + CMC 컨설팅)
- ❌ 임상 1상 진입 자격 = GLP-tox + GMP material + 안정성 + IND 승인 모두 cleared 상태
- ✅ 본 §15.6 = roadmap 으로서 paradigm 정의 (외부 진행 reference)

